<bibRefCitation author="Grove and Lavenberg" box="[500,811,1375,1401]" firstAuthor="Grove" pageId="175" pageNumber="176" refId="ref284033" refString="Grove, J. S. &amp; Lavenberg, R. J. (1997) The Fishes of the Galapagos Islands. Stanford University Press, Stanford." type="book" year="1997">Grove and Lavenberg 1997</bibRefCitation>
), and Gulf of California (Gomon in 
<bibRefCitation author="Fischer" box="[1213,1424,1374,1401]" etAl="et al." firstAuthor="Fischer" pageId="175" pageNumber="176" refId="ref278931" refString="Fischer, W., Krupp, F., Schneider, W., Sommer, C., Carpenter, K. E. &amp; Niem, V. H. (1995) Guia FAO para la identificacion para los fines de la pesca. Pacifico centro-oriental. Volume II, Vertebrados, Parte 1. Volume III, Vertebrados, Parte 2. FAO, Rome." type="book" year="1995">
